channel.title: StarzPk 317 Webclient Development Team!
channel.description:
Hello MoparScape, this is my new project called StarzPk. I'm looking to build up a new developing team for my RSPS. Post below if you are interested. We will be in need for a Web Developer, GFX Team, and one or two other developing partner who will like to code. I will be hosting the server and will attempt to give ideas to the server/client coders.
Server Developers: Open Spot
Client Developers Open Spot
Web Developer: Open Spot
GFX Team:
* Open Spot Open Spot Open Spot Open Spot
Server Goals: Have a stable and enjoyable server Create a great forums Community Provide People with a place were they can have a good time. Maintain a good player average
[code] How old are you? Name? How long have you been Programming?
What are you applying for?
Why should you be in development team?
Why would you like to be part of the team?
Any other information you wish can be added here.[/code]
[b]interested? PM or Reply[/b]
